
#Hotel room price calculator including tax.


name = input("Please enter your name: ")
print("Welcome Mr/Mrs. ", name)
rooms = int(input("How many rooms?: "))
price = float(input("Select price per room: ")) 
print("price per room is", price)
print("Number of rooms reserved: ", rooms) 
price = (price+(price*10/100))
total = rooms*price
print("Total price after 10% tax: ", total)


Output
------
Please enter your name: Kyi P Soe
Welcome Mr/Mrs.  Kyi P Soe
How many rooms?: 2
Select price per room: 65.95
price per room is 65.95
Number of rooms reserved:  2
Total price after 10% tax:  145.09
